# EndoCalc PWA

This repository now contains a GitHub Pages-friendly Progressive Web App version of Endo Tools.

## Features
- Endocrinology calculators grouped by category.
- Inspired UI matching https://johnyquest7.github.io/Endocrinology.io/ style.
- Installable from the browser (PWA) on desktop/mobile.
- Offline support with a service worker.

## Local run
Open `index.html` with a local web server for module loading (for example `python3 -m http.server 4173`).

## GitHub Pages
Publish the repository root on GitHub Pages. The app is static and requires no backend.
